2023-06-24 15:46:24.699 +02:00 [DBG] Generated query execution expression: 
'queryContext => ShapedQueryCompilingExpressionVisitor.SingleAsync<TmUsrUserAccount>(
    asyncEnumerable: new SingleQueryingEnumerable<TmUsrUserAccount>(
        (RelationalQueryContext)queryContext, 
        RelationalCommandCache.SelectExpression(
            Projection Mapping:
                UserCode -> 0
                UserName -> 1
                UserPw -> 2
                RoleCode -> 3
            SELECT TOP(1) t0.User_Code AS UserCode, t0.User_Name AS UserName, t0.User_Pw AS UserPw, t0.Role_Code AS RoleCode
